00:15:33.946 --> 00:15:35.577
I could do a spell.

00:15:35.579 --> 00:15:37.311
Yeah. When's that
ever worked, hmm?

00:15:37.313 --> 00:15:39.944
I know that most people
think it's bad,

00:15:39.946 --> 00:15:42.311
but all "the occult"
actually means is hidden.

00:15:42.313 --> 00:15:43.445
Oh.

00:15:43.447 --> 00:15:47.379
On a more
practical... note,

00:15:47.381 --> 00:15:49.713
a bit of...

00:15:49.715 --> 00:15:54.179
vigorous exercise
might get rid of it.

00:15:56.580 --> 00:15:59.247
Let's go dancing.

00:15:59.249 --> 00:16:03.247
Yeah. Where?

00:16:03.249 --> 00:16:04.914
Not far.

00:16:08.949 --> 00:16:10.448
Ha ha ha!

00:16:57.153 --> 00:16:59.585
Come on.

00:16:59.587 --> 00:17:01.552
Oh, I want you.
Come on.

00:17:01.554 --> 00:17:06.886
Come on.
Come to me.

00:17:06.888 --> 00:17:09.752
Come on. Uh!

00:17:13.221 --> 00:17:14.720
Come on.

00:17:26.121 --> 00:17:28.120
Uh...

00:17:57.924 --> 00:17:59.423
Um...

00:18:02.825 --> 00:18:04.557
Um...

00:18:10.591 --> 00:18:14.258
This situation has made
you so unpredictable.

00:18:14.260 --> 00:18:16.458
I'm sorry.

00:18:16.460 --> 00:18:18.391
I don't know what came over me.

00:18:23.893 --> 00:18:29.093
It's just, you're...

00:18:29.095 --> 00:18:30.759
you know, everything, and...

00:18:30.761 --> 00:18:33.959
And vise-a versa.

00:18:33.961 --> 00:18:37.293
It didn't mean a thing, truly.

00:18:37.295 --> 00:18:40.059
Oh... it's only
Kenneth.

00:18:45.895 --> 00:18:47.894
He went on about
the laws of love,

00:18:47.896 --> 00:18:50.861
