00:18:58.062 --> 00:19:00.961
And you told Susan
about your situation.

00:19:00.963 --> 00:19:04.929
I wanted shock on that
innocent, little face.

00:19:18.631 --> 00:19:22.830
I think I've wet myself.

00:19:22.832 --> 00:19:27.797
Uh, maybe you're losing it.

00:19:27.799 --> 00:19:32.731
No. It's just
a bit of, you know.

00:19:38.599 --> 00:19:43.965
He said the French call
an orgasm a small death.

00:19:43.967 --> 00:19:46.632
That's what it's like, you know.

00:19:46.634 --> 00:19:49.799
When a guy's inside you
and you get it right,

00:19:49.801 --> 00:19:53.466
feels like you're blacking out,

00:19:53.468 --> 00:19:54.699
dying.

00:21:24.908 --> 00:21:27.674
Abigail Mortimer

00:21:27.676 --> 00:21:31.674
