00:22:07.578 --> 00:22:10.645
Oh! For crying
out loud!

00:22:10.647 --> 00:22:15.111
Uh, uh... Janet,
go and get a mop.

00:22:15.113 --> 00:22:17.411
Oh...

00:22:26.747 --> 00:22:28.812
