It's legal nowadays.

00:23:12.585 --> 00:23:15.483
Not for the likes of us.

00:24:00.421 --> 00:24:02.587
Abbie?

00:24:09.088 --> 00:24:11.121
Ha ha ha!

00:24:25.690 --> 00:24:31.423
