from the ordinary fare."

00:25:02.761 --> 00:25:05.825
Keep thinking about keeping it.

00:25:05.827 --> 00:25:09.526
I know you don't want it.

00:25:09.528 --> 00:25:12.593
I'll get medical books
from the library, Morty.

00:25:12.595 --> 00:25:16.760
Nothing'll go wrong.
I know.

00:25:16.762 --> 00:25:18.260
It's just a feeling.

00:25:18.262 --> 00:25:20.294
But you can't trust feelings.

00:25:20.296 --> 00:25:22.594
We're not kids anymore, Lamb.

00:25:22.596 --> 00:25:23.861
We've got to face up to it.

00:25:23.863 --> 00:25:25.093
There's a real world out here.

00:25:25.095 --> 00:25:27.327
Yeah, and you're
the center of it.

00:25:27.329 --> 00:25:28.594
What's that?

00:25:28.596 --> 00:25:31.094
All this because he had a car,

00:25:31.096 --> 00:25:34.461
